data.description: Can't beat price per square footage and location! Well maintained home close to The Neuse Country Club, downtown Clayton, and much! Convenient to Highway 70 and I-40.  Fresh carpet, spacious kitchen, large living area, 2 car garage, first floor bedroom and so much more!
